1482: WITH consumptiondata AS (SELECT c.segment, SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END) AS total_consumption_2012, SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END) AS total_consumption_2013, SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END) AS consumption_increase, ((SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END)) / SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(y.date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN y.consumption ELSE 0 END)) * 100 AS percentage_increase FROM yearmonth AS y INNER JOIN customers AS c ON y.customerid = c.customerid WHERE c.currency = 'EUR' GROUP BY c.segment) SELECT segment, percentage_increase FROM consumptiondata WHERE percentage_increase = (SELECT MAX(percentage_increase) FROM consumptiondata) UNION ALL SELECT segment, percentage_increase FROM consumptiondata WHERE percentage_increase = (SELECT MIN(percentage_increase) FROM consumptiondata);	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
